---
layout: modern.njk
permalink: /papers/index.html
title: Publications
lang: ja
---

{%- set L = "ja" -%}

<!-- =================== PAGE HEAD =================== -->
<section class="page-head">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Publications</span>
    <h1>Publications</h1>
    <p class="lead">Starrydata プロジェクトの代表論文と、世界中の研究者による Starrydata の引用論文を掲載しています。OpenAlex + Crossref Open Citations から毎月自動更新。</p>
    <p class="papers-source">
      Sources:
      <a href="https://openalex.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">OpenAlex</a>
      ／
      <a href="https://opencitations.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener">OpenCitations</a>
      ／
      Last fetched: <time datetime="{{ papers.fetched_at }}">{{ papers.fetched_at.substring(0, 10) }}</time>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- =================== PROJECT PAPERS =================== -->
<section class="section section-top-tight" id="project-papers">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="papers-h2">
      Starrydata プロジェクト関連論文
      <span class="count">{{ papers.project_papers_count }}</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="papers-note">桂ゆかり氏らによる Starrydata プロジェクトの代表論文（DOI seed リストで管理）</p>

    <ol class="paper-list">
      {%- for p in papers.project_papers %}
      <li class="paper-item">
        <div class="paper-year-col">{{ p.year }}</div>
        <div class="paper-body">
          <p class="paper-title">
            {%- if p.doi_url %}
            <a href="{{ p.doi_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ p.title }}</a>
            {%- else %}
            {{ p.title }}
            {%- endif %}
          </p>
          {%- if p.authors %}<p class="paper-authors">{{ p.authors }}</p>{% endif %}
          <p class="paper-meta">
            {%- if p.journal %}<em class="journal">{{ p.journal }}</em>{% endif %}
            {%- if p.volume %} <strong>{{ p.volume }}</strong>{% endif %}
            {%- if p.issue %} [{{ p.issue }}]{% endif %}
            {%- if p.start_page %}, {{ p.start_page }}{% if p.end_page %}–{{ p.end_page }}{% endif %}{% endif %}
          </p>
          {%- if p.doi %}
          <p class="paper-doi">
            DOI: <a href="{{ p.doi_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ p.doi }}</a>
          </p>
          {%- endif %}
          {%- if p.cited_by_count %}
          <p class="paper-citations">
            <span class="citation-pill">Cited by <strong>{{ p.cited_by_count }}</strong>{% if p.cited_by_source == "crossref" %} (Crossref){% endif %}</span>
          </p>
          {%- endif %}
        </div>
      </li>
      {%- endfor %}
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- =================== CITING PAPERS =================== -->
<section class="section" id="citing-papers" style="background:#fff; border-top:1px solid var(--line); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="papers-h2">
      Starrydata を引用している論文
      <span class="count">{{ papers.citing_papers_count }}</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="papers-note">
      上記プロジェクト論文を引用している他研究者の論文（新しい順）。<br>
      Sources: OpenAlex only {{ papers.citing_papers_by_source.openalex_only }} ／
      OpenCitations only {{ papers.citing_papers_by_source.opencitations_only }} ／
      both {{ papers.citing_papers_by_source.both }}
    </p>

    {%- for group in papers.citing_papers_by_year %}
    <details class="year-group" {% if loop.first %}open{% endif %}>
      <summary class="year-summary">
        <span class="year-label">{{ group.year or 'Year unknown' }}</span>
        <span class="year-count">{{ group.count }} papers</span>
      </summary>
      <ol class="paper-list">
        {%- for p in group.papers %}
        <li class="paper-item paper-item-compact">
          <div class="paper-body">
            <p class="paper-title">
              {%- if p.doi_url %}
              <a href="{{ p.doi_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ p.title }}</a>
              {%- else %}
              {{ p.title }}
              {%- endif %}
            </p>
            {%- if p.authors %}<p class="paper-authors">{{ p.authors }}</p>{% endif %}
            <p class="paper-meta">
              {%- if p.journal %}<em class="journal">{{ p.journal }}</em>{% endif %}
              {%- if p.volume %} <strong>{{ p.volume }}</strong>{% endif %}
              {%- if p.issue %} [{{ p.issue }}]{% endif %}
              {%- if p.start_page %}, {{ p.start_page }}{% if p.end_page %}–{{ p.end_page }}{% endif %}{% endif %}
            </p>
            {%- if p.doi %}
            <p class="paper-doi">
              DOI: <a href="{{ p.doi_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ p.doi }}</a>
            </p>
            {%- endif %}
          </div>
        </li>
        {%- endfor %}
      </ol>
    </details>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
